OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy and dry through the evening
OL,7,Fwith some thicker cloud moving
OL,8,Fsouthwards along the coast overnight
OL,9,Fthat could give some localised light
OL,10,Frain or drizzle. A cooler night inland
OL,11,Fwith light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA mostly dry and cloudy day
OL,14,Ffor many, with potential for isolated
OL,15,Flight showers over the hills. Sunny
OL,16,Fspells developing through the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Mainly light winds.
OL,18,FTemperatures generally around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
